body:
Finally, I fixed the issue by doing the following: 
- backup (!) already deployed artifacts and cleanup /build folder;
- compile contracts with latest truffle (4.0.1), /build folder does not contain addresses after this step;
- move `networks` section from original artifacts to newly compiled by executing the quite simple [script](https://github.com/ChronoBank/SmartContracts/blob/release/release-1.1.43/scripts/update_artifact.js) (it might be needed to change file pathes)
- profit. works fine now.
